mahakavi kalidasu ( english : mahakavi ) is a 1960 telugu biographical film based on the life of the great mahabharata poet kalidas . the film stars akkineni nageswara rao , anjali devi in the lead roles and music composed by pendyala nageswara rao . starring akkineni nageswara rao , savitri in the lead roles and music composed by pendyala nageswara rao .